big_description = "Start combat in Mezzopiano
While in Mezzopiano:
- +60% Defense, -2 Moves
- Sound applies Alarmed, increasing Cog Speed

When hit by a Cog, gain 1 Accent for every 3 of its Speed points above yours
For each Accent, a random Gag becomes a Cue with -2 Cost
Use a Cue Gag to consume all Accent and enter Fortissimo

While in Fortissimo:
- -50% Gag Regen
- Gain +10% Damage and +2 Speed per Accent consumed"
